verbose_text: In addition, we correlated FADS2 expression with copy-number alterations, somatic mutations, and deletions of major oncogenes or tumor suppressors (MYC, PTEN, TP53, and PIK3CA) based on TCGA data from human cancers representing 33 major tumor types (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY A and S1B; XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY) and found significant correlations depending on the tumor type.
